    {
      "id": 361203,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "The physiologically active enantiomer of fluoxetine has (<i>S</i>) stereochemistry. Based on your answer in part <b>(a)</b>, draw the structure of the alkyl chloride you would need, showing the correct stereochemistry.",
